    "intent": "Decomposer-viability probe (issue #303). A productive producer stand reproduces and self-thins under light competition, raining structure-rich carcasses; a sessile decomposer embedded in the stand feeds on those carcasses. Exercises the producer->carcass->decomposer detrital pathway that no prior scenario reached.",
